snippet.title: Nullspace Official Teaser #2
snippet.description:
A glimpse of what's to come in NULLSPACE! 🌌

Experience a sleek new UI for seamless fleet control and witness the intensity of capital ship combat. Colossal warships, devastating firepower, and a larger, more tactical battlefield await! 

#nullspace #RTS #indiegamedev
